          "reviewBody": "My experience at this school has been wonderful. It’s a place where students are given plenty of opportunities to learn, grow, and excel in both academics and extracurricular activities.\n\nThe Teachers:\nThe teaching staff deserves special recognition for their dedication and professionalism. They make learning engaging and are always willing to help students who need extra support. Their encouragement has made a big difference in my confidence and understanding of the subjects.\n\nEnvironment:\nThe school provides a safe and supportive environment where every student feels included. The classrooms are well-maintained, and the overall atmosphere promotes focus and positivity.\n\nActivities and Facilities:\nThere’s a great balance between academics and extracurricular activities. The school offers excellent facilities for sports, arts, and science, ensuring that students can explore their interests beyond the classroom.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
